@startuml
title 13. MCP State Machine (Source Synchronized)

skinparam shadowing false

[*] --> received
received --> validated
validated --> planned
planned --> executing
executing --> finalized
finalized --> composing
composing --> completed
executing --> failed
composing --> failed

note right of validated
- key = session_id + request_id
- trace_id propagated
end note

note right of finalized
- tool results gathered
- history updated
end note

@enduml
